{"tid":2452949,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"應屆文憑試考生去年示威堵路罪成 鄭念慈判處120小時社會服務令","createTime":"2021-03-19T06:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T12:47:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"443adb31b3b981165d5e42a3612e1848f19400d9","tid":2452949,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14516&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSpLdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=99381c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14516</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第十三庭 <br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#20200510旺角 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n周(18)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n案情：2020年5月10日，在無合理解釋辯解下在旺角山東街59號公眾地方遺下三袋垃圾造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n被告先前已經認罪<br />\n<br />\n辯方陳詞：<br />\n被告明白及同意報告內容。被告內容正面，希望 感化官接納有真誠悔意。被告願意準從任何時數嘅社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官判刑：<br />\n報告內容正面，接受被告有悔意，以及出於衝動以及當時嘅行動係愚蠢行為。<br />\n<br />\n判處：‼️120小時社會服務令‼️"},{"pid":"89f1dd2088e315b8b7c19f42f11c6db14554ac3a","tid":2452949,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f210f75126a30a098026393fa021cad2c5449b1a","tid":2452949,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:57:32.000Z","msg":"都好<br />\n而家疫情都唔使趕住去油油，執垃圾<br />\n可以温下書先<br />\n如果諗住温書的話"},{"pid":"e598a67a70a591657ae6bb9cd9cf3ec88f5efd5d","tid":2452949,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n律正屍實上訴<br />\n然後上訴庭就送你去更生中心"},{"pid":"adda711f57b68e96d4ec25f489e8abdaedeec952","tid":2452949,"uid":289214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:59:28.000Z","m